cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CE, cs.IT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper is about the structure of the Internet at the autonomous system level. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper discusses the core and periphery of the network and how they relate to each other. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper describes new methods for plotting AS data. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possibility as the paper uses mathematical and computational methods to analyse the datasets. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper investigates the structure of the Internet and its properties.
